'''Graylite''' was a type of [[Ceramic/Legends|ceramic]]-fiber body [[Armor/Legends|armor]] produced by [[Opranko/Legends|Opranko]] and worn by members of the [[Balawai]] militia on [[Haruun Kal/Legends|Haruun Kal]]. It was rated against [[Gas/Legends|gas]] exposure, though the [[Nerve toxin/Legends|nerve agent]] [[Tisyn-C]] was not included in that rating.<ref name="SP">[[Shatterpoint (novel)|''Shatterpoint'']]</ref>

